snippet.title: SOUL REVERSE ZERO Android Gameplay [1080p/60fps]
snippet.description:
SOUL REVERSE ZERO (ソウルリバース ゼロ) by SEGA (RPG)
Uptodown | https://soul-reverse-zero.en.uptodown.com/android?utm_source=youtube.com&utm_medium=description&utm_campaign=traffic_ac
SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE HD VIDEOS → https://goo.gl/Pz1CBK
Google play | https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sega.srzero

Description | SOUL REVERSE ZERO is a JRPG with real-time combat system, in which players can guide a group of adventurers throughout a story full of magic, monsters and fantasy. The game also includes special events in which we can play with the popular anime characters such as Fairy Tail.
